title: Suicides in Sweden in 2018 , by gender and age group
summary: The statistic shows the Suicides Sweden 2018 in the Sweden in 2018 , age group .
In 2018 , about 110 % of the respondents aged 291 to 29 years old .
gold: The highest number of suicides in Sweden in 2018 was committed among men from 14 to 44 years , amounting to 361 suicides.
The corresponding figure among women in this age group was 151 , a significantly lower number.
For all age groups , more suicides were committed among men than among women .
